fields.name: Langstroth 10-frame
fields.description:
The Langstroth system is widely used internationally.

Such systems generally come in three widths, all of which use identical frames: 
Boxes with capacity for 10 Langstroth frames.
Boxes with capacity for 8 Langstroth frames.
Boxes with capacity for 5 Langstroth frames.

The width measurements are the only measures that differ between the system. The length and height measurements are identical.

fields.name: Langstroth 8-frame
fields.description:
The Langstroth system is widely used internationally. Such systems generally come in three widths, all of which use identical frames: Boxes with capacity for 10 Langstroth frames, boxes with capacity for 8 Langstroth frames and boxes with capacity for 5 Langstroth frames.

The width measurements are the only measures that differ between the system. The length and height measurements are identical.

fields.name: Langstroth 5-frame
fields.description:
The Langstroth system is widely used internationally. Such systems generally come in three widths, all of which use identical frames: Boxes with capacity for 10 Langstroth frames. Boxes with capacity for 8 Langstroth frames. Boxes with capacity for 5 Langstroth frames. The width measurements are the only measures that differ between the system. The length and height measurements are identical.

5-frame boxes are often used for newly created colonies, and are sometimes referred to as colony nuclei (or nucs for short).
